dc_title_s: Streams, Rivers, and Canals: Ensenada, Mexico, 2010
dc_description_s: This line shapefile represents streams (arroyos), rivers (rios), and canals (canales) in Ensenada (Mexico). LeadDog Consulting (Originator and Publisher) has a Mexico-based data partner network for which they have access to GIS data sets to create city streets maps for Mexico, which may include streets, street names, street classifications, points of interests, landuse, water, neighborhood points, and railroads. These data are intended for geographic display and analysis at the city level. No responsibility is assumed by LeadDog Consulting. Instituto Nacional de Estadística, Geografía e Informática (Mexico) and LeadDog Consulting. (2010). Streams, Rivers, and Canals: Ensenada, Mexico, 2010. LeadDog Consulting Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/wq349kn9745
